        <item>
            <title>Honda 将 Pokemon 实体化成电单车，灵感来自《Pokemon 朱》神兽 Koraidon</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/honda-pokemon-koraidon/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honda-pokemon-koraidon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/honda-pokemon-koraidon/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 06:14:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Honda]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294639</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本本田技研工业（Honda）与 Pokémon 公司合作，推出以《Pokémon 朱》传说神兽「故勒顿」（Koraidon）为蓝本的实体电单车「Honda 故勒顿」。这款几乎等比例的未来主义车种将于 2025 年 3 月 7 日至 3 月 9 日，在东京本田青山迎宾广场展出。Honda 表示，该项目结合尖端技术，力求还原故勒顿的设计与特性。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「Honda 故勒顿」在尺寸与重量上贴近游戏中的设定，并融入本田独有的自平衡技术。此技术源于 2017 年 CES 展公开的「Honda Riding Assist」，借鉴 ASIMO 机器人的平衡控制原理。据本田透露，未来版本有望实现故勒顿的「疾驰形态」及四足行走功能，展现动态魅力。展览期间虽未提供试驾，但其细腻设计已令人期待。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>据日媒报导，Toyota 于 2024 年曾推出《Pokemon 紫》的神兽「密勒顿」（Miraidon）实体电单车，开启车厂与 Pokémon 合作的先河。Honda 今次以「Koraidon」为题，似有与对手一较高下之意。业界人士分析，Honda 凭借机车制造经验，或能在技术层面超越 Toyota 的展示型设计，进一步提升实用性与观赏性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「Honda 故勒顿」展示技术实力之余，也标志著动漫文化与汽车工业的深度融合。展览过后，业界预料 Honda 或会进一步完善此概念车，甚至探索量产可能。随著 Pokémon 热潮持续，未来或有更多车厂加入这场创意竞赛，为市场带来新惊喜。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_12249"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ryoEWpD9NMg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cool-style.com.tw/wd2/archives/1167841-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%84%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%EF%BC%81honda-%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A2-%E6%9C%B1%E3%80%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%8D%B8%E3%80%8C%E6%95%85%E5%8B%92%E9%A0%93%E3%80%8D">COOL</a>、<a href="https://www.siliconera.com/honda-teases-pokemon-koraidon-appearance-in-real-life/">siliconear</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
