        <item>
            <title>小米 15 Ultra 发表: 首部支持奥斯卡 ACES 电影色彩系统 Android 手机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-15-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:35:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294557</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米于 2025 年 2 月 27 日晚正式发布旗舰机型 Xiaomi 15 Ultra，搭载 Snapdragon 8 Elite 处理器，售价由 6,499 人民币起。新机主打 Leica 四摄系统，其中 200MP 远摄镜头备受瞩目，并推出拼色设计向 Leica 致敬。国际版将于 3 月在巴塞隆纳 MWC 大会亮相，香港上市详情待公布。</p><h2></h2><h2>外观与设计</h2><p>Xiaomi 15 Ultra 延续圆形相机模组设计，推出黑、白、黑银及绿银四款配色，其中拼色版本灵感源自 Leica 相机，背面采用荔枝皮纹理。机身重 226g，厚 9.35mm，具 IP68 防尘防水功能，并支援双喇叭及四咪高风配置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q-694x489.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="489" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q-694x489.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q.jpeg 1278w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2-694x496.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2-694x496.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2.jpeg 1002w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b-694x578.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b-694x578.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b.jpeg 1013w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>专业影像体验</h2><p>新机配备 Leica 四摄系统（14-100mm），包括 1 吋  50MP Sony LYT-900 主摄及 200MP Samsung HP9 远摄镜头，4 镜，光学焦距等效 14mm / 23mm / 70mm / 100mm。支援 28 倍无损变焦及 8K 录影，另有专属影像套装，包括滤镜转接环及具 2,000mAh 电池的握把，提升拍摄灵活性。在拍片方面，小米是 Android 首部支持奥斯卡 ACES 电影色彩系统</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5-694x365.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5-694x365.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>规格与性能</h2><p>配备 6.73 吋 2K+ AMOLED 萤幕，亮度达 3,200 尼特，支援 120Hz LTPO。电池容量 6,000mAh，提供 90W 有线及 80W 无线充电。处理器为 Snapdragon 8 Elite，搭配 LPDDR5X RAM 与 UFS 4.1 储存。随 MWC 临近，更多细节或将公布，值得关注其本地定价与发售安排。</p><h2>官方样本</h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1-399x580.jpeg" alt="" width="399" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1-399x580.jpeg 399w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1.jpeg 618w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 399px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294570" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/">小米 15 Ultra 发表: 首部支持奥斯卡 ACES 电影色彩系统 Android 手机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
